Frequently Asked Questions about Bay Area Pizza

Does Bay Area Pizza take reservations?

Yes, you can make a reservation by picking a date, time, and party size.

Does Bay Area Pizza have outdoor seating?

Yes, Bay Area Pizza has outdoor seating.

Is Bay Area Pizza currently offering delivery or takeout?

Yes, Bay Area Pizza offers both delivery and takeout.

What forms of payment are accepted?

Bay Area Pizza accepts credit cards.
